Package org.cougaar.core.mobility.ldm

Interface Summary
AgentControl Request an agent management operation, as defined in the AgentControl.getAbstractTicket().
MobilityFactory A Factory for creating AgentControl objects.
MoveAgent A request that an agent be moved from its current node to a different node.
 

Class Summary
MobilityDomain This component is the mobility domain, which just has the MobilityFactory and no LogicProviders.
MoveAgent.Status Immutable class that represents the dynamic status of the move request.
TicketIdentifier A unique ticket identifier generated by the MobilityFactory.
